*vdr-1.2.6-r4

  7 Jan 2004; H.Ryll <henning.ryll@web.de>
  Optional 256 Color OSD added VDR_OPTS=256color

  27 Dez 2003; M.Hierling <mad@cc.fh-lippe.de>
  fixed some typos
  added full path to all binarys
  added VDR_OPTS emergeplugs for automatically emerge of all used plugins (read wiki!)
  qpkg change output to uncolored for use with emerge
  changed all patch stuff to epatch (not that much unwanted output, only nice green [OK] )

  27 Dez 2003; H.Ryll <henning.ryll@web.de>
  Update to Improved OSD 3a

  7 Jan 2004; H.Ryll <henning.ryll@web.de>
  Optional 256 Color OSD added

  24 Dez 2003; F.Schilhabel <fernsehleo@gmx.net>
  initial import of r4 with new logic w/o gentoo-patch(es)

*vdr-1.2.6-r3
  13 Dez 2003; H.Ryll <henning.ryll@web.de>
  Now including new Complete-Patch "B" with improved OSD
  based on version 1.2.6 (not r1 or r2)
  Hopefully solving Problems with scanner.c

  14 Dez 2003; H.Ryll <henning.ryll@web.de>
  Now including new Complete-Patch "C" with improved OSD
  Improved OSD now works with elchi-patch too

*vdr-1.2.6-r2
