*vdr-1.2.0 (04 Jun 2003)
  03 Jul 2003; M.Hierling <mad@cc.fh-lippe.de>
  renamed vdr_vfat to vfat 

  01 Jul 2003; M.Hierling <mad@cc.fh-lippe.de>
  fixed download location of akool patch

  20 Jun 2003; M.Hierling <mad@cc.fh-lippe.de>
  added AD3overDVB patch, contributed by trtr-z

  04 Jun 2003; M.Hierling <mad@cc.fh-lippe.de>
  jumped to version 1.2.0, vdr now runs with uid vdr and gid video,
  pluginnames changed, some default dirs changed, added default
  plugins, moved plugindir to /usr/lib/vdr 
  added VDR_OPTS (vfat, rcu, akool) to steer the installation of
  patches and vdr addons
  added vdrshutdown.sh sample script

