*vdr-1.1.25-r3 (15 Mar 2003)
  15 Mar 2003; M.Hierling <mad@cc.fh-lippe.de> vdr-1.1.25-r3.ebuild
  added use variable for VFAT (USE="vdr_vfat")
  added use variable for Elchi AIO (USE="vdr_elchi")
  The supplied Elchi 1.1.25 patch is nothing new, it is the
  1.1.20 patch but packed new to be applied without the nasty
  ofset warnings

*vdr-1.1.25-r2 (14 Mar 2003)
